main event: A UFO report describes the observation of five elongated lights changing direction and brightness over Trenton, New Jersey for 20 minutes.
interesting points: Witness reported the objects changing from one to five lights during observation,The lights appeared star-like with bluish-green edges and light orange centers,Objects were observed to perform abrupt 90-degree turns,The sighting occurred on a clear night with good visibility,The observer had a background as a contractor-builder and was previously an engineer.
sighted object: five elongated lights in the sky
witness description: Civilian contractor-builder, former engineer in P-24 aircraft.
